text: Cova Lima is a municipality in East Timor. The capital of the municipality is Suai. Cova Lima borders the Timor Sea to the south. The administrative posts of Cova Lima are: * Fatululic * Fatumean * Fohorem * Zumalai * Maucatar * Suai * Tilomar Category:Municipalities of East Timor
title: Cova Lima Municipality
